- Use interceptors for global request/response handling
- Implement proper error handling and retries for failed requests
- Utilize Axios' cancel token feature for aborting requests
- Set appropriate timeouts for different types of requests
- Create reusable API service modules
- Implement proper request caching strategies
- Use proper authentication handling
- Handle response data transformation consistently 